attributionInfo.brokerName: Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties
Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure II

data.description: Looking for the perfect Nest in the perfect location?! Look no further! This 3 story home is located only minutes from beautiful North Carolina beaches as well as MARSOC Stone Bay and MCB Camp LeJeune Sneads Ferry gates! Downstairs the open floor plan is perfect for entertaining. Head up stairs to the second story where you will find the large primary suite and two very nice sized guest bedrooms that share a Jack and Jill bathroom. Finally, head up to the 3rd floor where you'll find a spacious area that could be used as a bedroom, a family room, or game room complete with it's own full bathroom. Sit and relax in the large fenced backyard with storage shed perfect for summer BBQ's and fall bonfires.
